name: SKATEBOARDING, PT. III
description: What is the essence of skateboarding? Is it the freedom? Is it the endless creativity? Is it element of danger? Is it the thrill of victory? Is it the wind on your face on a warm summer day? Is it the feeling of new wheels on perfectly smooth cement? Is it smiles on friends faces? Is it crazy people we meet as we skate through the city? Is it that moment you realize you got that amazing trick on lock and the next game of S.K.A.T.E. you know you're going to win? Is it the joy of seeing young children, teens & adults alike point in unison and say, "Cooooooooooool"? Yes, and so much more.
